  <brief_title>An Observational Study of RoActemra/Actemra in Patients With Moderate to Severe Rheumatoid Arthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicenter REtrospective Study to Evaluate coMpliance to Therapy and Drug survIval of Tocilizumab (TCZ) in patientS With Moderate to Severe actIve rheumatOid Arthritis in routiNe Daily Clinical Practice (REMISSION Study)</official_title>
