  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This open-label, retrospective, observational study will evaluate the compliance to
      RoActemra/Actemra (tocilizumab) therapy in patients with moderate to severe rheumatoid
      arthritis. Six months data will be collected from patients records.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
